snippet.title: BUBBLE BOBBLE (Luxury Re-release / 2 Loading screens / Trainer options) Walkthrough, ZX Spectrum
snippet.description:
Huge playlist archive with games from 1982-1992: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLxOanVBhqd3uy0uOIHzPaxfOp53uJLX7-
Many more games from the 80s can be found here:
Racing games: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLxOanVBhqd3vkkE35mCw6x63QFBnU9Xsi
AY / GFX improved games: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLxOanVBhqd3t74YnYAJA9p4vMQYZYCJWX

Updated 2015 version with Neil Parsons new loading screen based on Taito's arcade videogame poster, and trainer options made by Slider. It is a Beta Disk version and SCL and TRD files can be downloaded here: https://vtrd.in/release.php?r=f7cd0ac520e16a4fdfd770aa1497f81e
